April 3, 2020
Today, we're explaining how the speed at which the U.S. economy recovers from coronavirus depends on how things "shape up." That's followed by some geographic trivia and a trip to the world's second-largest desert. And we're showing you how sled dogs are helping make important deliveries for elderly people in Maine.
